moji\" /> 0x無限 唔會等於12/6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nup乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你會覺得一個數除以0會係無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你講法係6/0 = 12/0 = &infin;<br />\n<br />\n移一移項咪變咗0*&infin; = 6, 0*&infin; = 12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndividend / divisor = quotient<br />\n<br />\nquotient * divisor = dividend<br />\n<br />\n除係乘嘅逆運算 咁將quotient同divisor用乘砌返出嚟應該會得出dividend 咁樣驗證個答案唔係infinity應該小學都有學架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁又數學家 有嘢你咪講 你咁樣同擺低粒膠就走咗去有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係幫條on9 <br />\n只係有班on 9冇用做既數學家唔想除0既時候冇意義/error 所以定義左 x/0既時候 0只係無限接近0 所以會出無限 但其他時間都係0</blockquote><br />\nSource?<br />\n<br />\n0就係0 係0嘅話就幾時都係0<br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢除0嘅時就唔係0 咁原本個definition咪錯撚晒 咪乜撚都亂撚晒<br />\n<br />\n用limit嗰陣 無限接近0就係無限接近0 0就係0 你搞清楚 咪撚撈埋一齊 乜撚嘢其他時間先係0 垃撚圾<br />\n<br />\n數學唔係咁樣畀你亂嚟定義 唔識就收返你啲廢話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.khanacademy.org/math/algebra/introduction-to-algebra/division-by-zero/v/why-dividing-by-zero-is-undefined\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khanacademy.org%2Fmath%2Falgebra%2Fintroduction-to-algebra%2Fdivision-by-zero%2Fv%2Fwhy-dividing-by-zero-is-undefined&d=MeBvb6vMKKOPM7%2BcP9u4gAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=55d9aebd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.khanacademy.org/math/algebra/introduction-to-algebra/division-by-zero/v/why-dividing-by-zero-is-undefined</a>"},{"pid":"091431ae0187f807d6172ba2c81d43f06c1e8424","tid":410674,"uid":66779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Infinity is a concept <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁樣擺句係人都知嘅嘢出嚟係唔會解決到任何問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好 我擺infinity喺條式入面係貪咗快<br />\n<br />\n咁換個講法 10除2=5嘅另一種表達方式就係5個2加埋等於10<br />\n<br />\n咁如果12係0嘅無限倍 咪變咗無限個0加埋係12 做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面條戇鳩又係 無限個無限接近0嘅0相加就會變成12？<br />\n<br />\n又係做乜鳩 兩嚿無限細嘅嘢相加 點睇都係會得出另一嚿無限細嘅嘢 點會加加下就唔係無限細<br />\n<br />\n屌 睇嚟我都係弱智先會同你兩條弱智拗"},{"pid":"58d3df265436ccdbea6a24dfab85963aedf6e8ab","tid":410674,"uid":119008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"樓主呢d垃圾早死早著"},{"pid":"de4ce36158fb4fed9275a64b4b092cbddbd0c8c4","tid":410674,"uid":63782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T20:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2012 DSE狀元 港大：6 中大：0<br />\n2013 DSE狀元 港大：7 中大：2<br />\n2014 DSE狀元 港大：9 中大：3<br />\n2015 DSE狀元 港大：12 中大：0<br />\n2016 DSE狀元 港大：3 中大：1<br />\n2017 DSE狀元 港大：5 中大：1<br />\n代表D咩?</blockquote><br />\n2012同2015年港大收到既DSE狀元係中大既無限倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n文科仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 0x無限 唔會等於12/6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nup乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你會覺得一個數除以0會係無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你講法係6/0 = 12/0 = &infin;<br />\n<br />\n移一移項咪變咗0*&infin; = 6, 0*&infin; = 12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndividend / divisor = quotient<br />\n<br />\nquotient * divisor = dividend<br />\n<br />\n除係乘嘅逆運算 咁將quotient同divisor用乘砌返出嚟應該會得出dividend 咁樣驗證個答案唔係infinity應該小學都有學架喎<img src=\"/assets/face